  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Overview&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    When creating test scripts, you will find that some steps are prime candidates for reuse. The ability to simply drag&#xD;
    and drop step content from one test script to another that you are working on can dramatically improve the efficiency&#xD;
    of the test script development process.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    One of the key features of IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Manual Tester is the ability to easily reuse content from a test script. When&#xD;
    you are executing test scripts, you can build test scripts more efficiently by reusing test script content from&#xD;
    previous scripts. In Rational Manual Tester, you can take statements from a given test script -- that you know will be&#xD;
    reused in other test scripts -- and store them for reuse.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Tool Steps&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    To reuse content form a test script, perform the following steps:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ol>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Open the script containing the content that you want to reuse&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        In the Outline view, select the given statement, statements, or group of statements that you want to reuse&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Drag your selection to the Reuse view&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Create a new script (see the &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithType&quot; href=&quot;./../../../core.tech.common.extend_rmt-ibm/guidances/toolmentors/create_man_test_script_C37BC28B.html&quot; guid=&quot;_dAngsHj0EdyhRNciHt44hg&quot;>Tool Mentor: Create Test Scripts Using IBM Rational Manual Tester&lt;/a>)&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        In the Reuse view, select the step you want to reuse and drag it to the Outline view. The Outline view and Text&#xD;
        Editor are automatically updated&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Save your new script&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ol>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    &lt;img height=&quot;16&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;./resources/helpbook.gif&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; /> For more information on reusing test script&#xD;
    content, see the topic &lt;em>Saving and Reusing Test Statements&lt;/em> in the Rational Manual Tester online Help.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
